No. 09-9165. Mike Redford, Petitioner v. Collier Heights Apartments, et al. 559 U.S. 1047, 130 S. Ct. 2352, 2010 U.S. LEXIS 2967.

176 L. Ed. 2d 559,

April 5, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of Georgia dismissed. See Rule 39.8.

Same case below, 298 Ga. App. 116, 679 S.E.2d 120.
